::GoldenEye::
She walked out and stood next to DarkMouse,"What's going on?"

DarkMouse::
"There's someone here to talk to KitKat."

GoldenEye::
"Well, let's hope this one is a good fighter. We're going to need a 
good fighter. I have a bad feeling about this up coming fight."

DarkMouse::
"I don't.  I'm just hoping that we win. I'd hate to go to the 
Allience as a slave or something. I'd rather get killed."

GoldenEye::
"Not me.  I'd rather spend some time with Dollen."

DarkMouse::
"Who?"

GoldenEye::
"Dollen.  He..Oh never mind.  You'll see him when he get's here."

DarkMouse::
She shrugged her shoulders. "OK, but I still hope we win."
She looked out, waiting for this bot to approach.  She was wondering 
who had the nerve to just walk up and they wanted to talk to the 
leader.

GoldenEye::
"So who are we waiting on?"

DarkMouse::
"Ehh, some bot who wants to talk to KitKat. She's busy so I get to 
play tour guild until she's ready for who ever this bot is."
She still had her sidearm ready, but down at her side.
